               <p>Yesterday week I was standing to see a procession of the Free British Society, at the end of <placeName id="t17900707-4-crimeloc22">Red Cross-street, near Barbican</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900707-4-crimeloc22" type="placeName" value="Red Cross-street, near Barbican"></interp>
